# Handoff — Pack #5 (Knowledge Engine) Phase 1 complete

## What was done

**Phase 1 (Write path) of Pack #5
(`knowledge-engine-json-store`) is
code-complete.** The full write path is
implemented end-to-end: the JSON+Markdown
adapter validates input, generates a v4
UUID `RecordId`, slugifies the topic, writes
the file atomically (temp + fsync + rename +
parent fsync), updates the in-memory search
index, and publishes a `KnowledgeRecordStored`
audit event on the bus. The other two trait
methods (`find_information` and `list_topics`)
are stubs returning
`KnowledgeErrorV1::CapabilityUnsupported`
(their real bodies land in Phase 2).

