## Work ethics followed

- Story-telling comments on every
  non-trivial function (the "plain
  English first" rule from
  [PHILOSOPHY.md](file:///home/spanexx/Shared/agents/PHILOSOPHY.md)).
- CID headers on every new type and
  function.
- No fake / tautological tests — every
  test asserts on observable behavior
  (file system, index state, bus events).
- Validation gate is the single-command
  `make check` entry point.
- Logging was kept to the work itself
  (the prompt log was appended once at
  session start).
